name: NATPlus
description: NATP is a innovative option issued by the C-计划 platform. The vision of NATP is to build a future digital society community that coexists with the virtual and real worlds, where new technologies such as big data, artificial intelligence, and blockchain are deeply integrated and applied. Using a completely digital operating model, NATP digitizes tangible and intangible assets, as well as real-world economic application scenarios, to provide digital empowerment for people's owned assets, certificates, abilities, and other tangible and intangible assets.
